    @Internal
public abstract class KryoRegistrationSerializerConfigSnapshot<T>
extends GenericTypeSerializerConfigSnapshot<T>
    Configuration snapshot base class for serializers that use Kryo for serialization.

    The configuration captures the order of Kryo serializer registrations, so that new Kryo serializers can determine how to reconfigure their registration order to retain backwards compatibility.
